Marbleman
'''Marbleman''' is a fat [[13-year-old boy|12-year-old kid]] from Virginia who posted a video on [[YouTube]] about "[[meme|may-mays]]", "[[desu|deh-zoo]]", and "ee tee see" (for etc.). Days later, a user posted his [[Stickam]] account to [[/b/]], after which 4chan [[troll]]ed him to [[in the ass|oblivion]].

